%% Kubeflow Notebook Controller - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as ODH Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KFCtrl as kf-notebook-controller<br/>controller-runtime
    participant ODHCtrl as odh-notebook-controller<br/>controller-runtime
    participant OAuthSrv as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant CullCtrl as Culling Controller

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-notebook-v1<br/>TLS, API server cert
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: GET ImageStream<br/>SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Image reference
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook<br/>(oauth-proxy injected, CA bundles, env vars)
    K8sAPI-->>User: Notebook created

    Note over KFCtrl,Notebook: kf-notebook-controller Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>KFCtrl: Watch event: Notebook
    KFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>SA Token
    KFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>SA Token

    Note over ODHCtrl,OAuthSrv: odh-notebook-controller Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>ODHCtrl: Watch event: Notebook
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>SA Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>SA Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OAuthClient<br/>SA Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OAuth Secrets<br/>SA Token
    ODHCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount + RoleBinding<br/>SA Token

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: Notebook Access (OAuth Enabled)
    User->>Router: GET https://{notebook-route}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward (TLS reencrypt)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthSrv: OAuth flow<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth Client Credentials
    OAuthSrv-->>OAuthProxy: OAuth Token
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: SAR check:<br/>verb=get, resource=notebooks
    OAuthProxy->>Notebook: Forward request<br/>8888/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    Notebook-->>OAuthProxy: Response
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: Response (HTTPS)
    Router-->>User: Response (HTTPS)

    Note over CullCtrl,Notebook: Flow 3: Idle Notebook Culling
    CullCtrl->>Notebook: GET /api/kernels<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    Notebook-->>CullCtrl: Kernel status
    CullCtrl->>Notebook: GET /api/terminals<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    Notebook-->>CullCtrl: Terminal status
    alt Notebook is idle
        CullCtrl->>K8sAPI: PATCH annotation<br/>(kubeflow-resource-stopped)<br/>SA Token
        KFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Scale StatefulSet to 0<br/>SA Token
    end
